                        <interp inst="t18570615-name-329" type="given" value="JONATHAN"></interp>JONATHAN WHITCHER</persName>
                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">repeated his evidence given in the last case.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18570615-725-verdict-1" type="verdictDescription">
