                  </hi>. (<hi rend="italic">City policeman</hi>, 493). I produce a certificate of the prisoner's conviction—(<hi rend="italic">Read: "Central Criminal Court, May</hi>, 1856; <hi rend="italic">James Beaumont, Convicted of stealing a purse and an order for the payment of money; 
Confined one year</hi>")—I was present—the prisoner is the man.</p>
